      "text": "Which one of the following is an enrichment medium?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Alkaline peptone water"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Monsur's taurocholate tellurite peptone water"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Selenite F broth"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "All of the above"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer D - All of the above</strong><strong> </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Enrichment Broth:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Liquid media with <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1b6bd49bf11692777190214aa47f99\">inhibitory</span> agents selectively promote the growth of specific organisms and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"6b3de87b7c16927771901326efbcd2\">inhibit</span> others.</li>\n\t<li>Used for isolating pathogens from clinical specimens containing normal <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0af84af4761692777202fbf6914573\">flora</span> (e.g., stool, sputum).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Examples:</strong></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>Tetrathionate <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"46988d61a21692777183ac440c691a\">broth</span> – Used for <em>Salmonella Typhi</em> isolation.</li>\n\t<li>Gram-negative <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"46988d61a21692777183ac440c691a\">broth</span> – Used for <em>Shigella</em> isolation.</li>\n\t<li>Selenite F <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"46988d61a21692777183ac440c691a\">broth</span> – Used for <em>Shigella</em> isolation. <strong>(Option C)</strong></li>\n\t<li>Alkaline <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"34686cea521692777195ce0fbb7f69\">peptone</span> water (APW) – Used for <em>Vibrio cholerae</em> isolation. <strong>(Option A)</strong></li>\n\t<li><strong>Lim Broth</strong> is an <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ba325c18481692777187ae8d082f45\">enrichment</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"46988d61a21692777183ac440c691a\">broth</span> specifically used to enhance the growth of group B streptococci. It provides the necessary nutrients and conditions for the selective <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ea15a8dedc1692777193399f05b191\">multiplication</span> of these organisms.</li>\n\t<li>Monsur's <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"d32711977216927772004e0d680631\">taurocholate</span> tellurite <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"34686cea521692777195ce0fbb7f69\">peptone</span> water <strong>(Option B)</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<ol>\n</ol>",
